task.summary: Default task
Address input front-end mostly done
Redesigned login to use material-ui. Needs to respond correctly to 'enter' press
Updated Sign Up form to use material-ui
New Student form upgraded. Has some styling issues
Removed unused imports. Added email to student view
Added more comprehensive address table to teacher and student records.
Updated front-end to make use of updated address field in backend
Appointments from outside of the month no longer appear on calendar view
Added checkboxes to the calendar to display attended/payed
Calendar bookings are now greyed out when cancelled
Cancelled Calendar bookings are now strikethrough
Booking changed to function component
Basic Booking redesign
Further improved booking. Uses the booking object rather than passing individual parts of booking to props. Still uses attended+payed temporarily to simplify logic.
Invoice fixed. Added printable address to AddressResource to stop doubling effort
Simplfy/redisign of daily view
Menu is now Popover. TopBar redesigned
Hero image up
CTA added to hero
Created LogInButton and SignUpButton components which create SignUp and LogIn modals
Home Page Route working. Style fixes - changed some components from css to MakeStyles
Added nifty chevrons to day and week navigators
Hero text changed, media-query size requirements changed, note-to-self added
Added config.js which currently stores the server url, and updated components to use config
Moved weekNavigator.css into makeStyles
Changed day navigator buttons to link-style
Added wrap to app to stop elements overhanging the left screen edge when more than 100% wide
TopBar cleaned up a little.
Elements will now display full size on mobile, though users should be dissuaded from certain views on mobile
Added arrows to go up or back one week in dayNavigator. Don't fully work
Changed dayNavigator to use date-fns for date formatting
Login Displays errors on bad input and doesn't let invalid users pass
Login button disabled until user enter username and password
Changed Login over to use react-hook-form Added Double-chevrons to dayNavigator
Header (topBar) is a bit responsive now
topBar more responsive. topBar.css removed
Added Sign Out icon. Tidied Kanban
Weekly forwards/backwards buttons now work on Daily view
Modals switched to Dialogs to get around forwardRef error
Added DayOrWeek test component
Invoice data responds to cancelled lessons. Backend updated to support this
Cleaned KanBan
Cancelled lesson bookings are greyed out
Made bookings smaller
Buttons get thinner on smaller screens. (Trying to fit in a weekly view on a mobile device)
Added phone number to student overview
Added StudentBrowser component
Added Student browser to menu
Daily view styled a little better
